    "question": "Which word order is the usual way to say \"I do not speak Spanish\"?",
    "correctAnswer": "{{es-ES|No hablo español.||NO HA-blo es-pa-NOL.}}",
    "incorrectAnswers": [
      "{{es-ES|Hablo no español.||HA-blo NO es-pa-NOL.}}",
